2. Gii Thiu

  • Nhng yu t c lin quan n vic mua hng ti ca hng ?

  • T l chp nhn cc chin dch tip th theo tng khu vc ?
    • Xy dng biu ngi xem c ci nhn trc quan v t l chp nhn cc chin dch.
  • Chin dch tip th thnh cng nht ?
    • Trc quan ha c ci nhn v chin dch no hot ng tt,thnh cng.
  • Phng thc bn hng no km hiu qu nht ?
    • Trc quan d liu thy phng thc no tht bi trong chin dch ny.
  • Quc gia c tng s ln mua hng v chi tiu cao nht ?
    • Trc quan ho d liu xem mc chi tiu cao nht ca cc vng v a ra cc sn phm ph hp.
  • Sn phm no chim doanh thu nhiu nht ?
    • Xy dng biu thy c sn phm no bn chy v mang v doanh thu tt.
  • D on mc chi tiu ca khch hng da trn thu nhp c nhn, tng s lt mua hng, tnh trng hn nhn

  • D on kh nng chp nhn chin dch ca khch hng da vo lt mua hng, thu nhp, tnh trng hn nhn, s con trong gia nh,
    • T m hnh hc my d on kh nng chp nhn chin dch
      • chun on cn input l 14 bin:(Income, Education, Recency, MntWines, MntFruits, MntMeatProducts, MntFishProducts, MntSweetProducts, MntGoldProds, NumDealsPurchases, NumWebPurchases, NumCatalogPurchases, NumStorePurchases, NumWebVisitsMonth)

4. Trc quan ha d liu (data visulization)

  • 4.1 T l chp nhn cc chin dch phn theo vng ?
    • T biu trn,ta c th thy rng t l chp nhn ca cc chin dch 1,3,4,5 trn khp tt c cc quc gia gn gn ging nhau (ngoi tr quc gia ME)
    • C 3 vng AUS, ME, US cha chp nhn chin dich s 2 ta nn xut chin dch tng ng tng t l chp nhn trn cc quc gia
  • 4.2 Phng thc bn hng no hiu qu nht ?
    • T biu trn,ta c th thy rng s ln mua hng trc tip ti ca hng v mua trc tuyn chim t l cao. Trong mua hng ti ca hng c a chung
    • S ln mua hng theo danh mc v s ln mua hng c gim gi cn kh thp. Do cn phi a ra cc chin lc qung co trn truyn thng thu ht s ch ca nhiu khch hng hn
  • 4.3 Sn phm no mang li doanh thu cao nht cho ca hng ?
    • C th thy trong c cu doanh thu th Ru chim t trng cao nht, tip theo l Tht v Vng
    • D dng nhn thy cc chin dch trn 3 dng sn phm ny kh tt. T nn y mnh chin dch marketing v ang din ra trn 3 sn phm ny.
  • 4.4 Chin dch no thc hin v mang li thnh cng ?
    • D dng nhn thy trong s c chin dch marketing thc hin th chin dch s 3, 4 cho kt qu tt hn cc chin dch cn li
    • Cn Chin dch 2 l chin dch t nht.
    • Cn loi b chin dch 2 ra khi chin dch tip th.
    • Cn cng c v u t thm cho 2 chin dch 3 v 4. Ci thin chin dch 1 v 5 mang li kt qu tt hn.

5. M hinh hoa d liu ( data modeling )

  • 5.1 Xy dng m hnh d on mc chi tiu da vo b d liu marketing_data.csv
    • M hnh hi quy tuyn tnh (linear regression): f(x)=w1x1 + w2x2 + w3x3 +wnxn +w0
    • Linear regression l: Mt phng php thng k hi quy d liu vi bin ph thuc c gi tr lin tc trong khi cc bin c lp c th c mt trong hai gi tr lin tc hoc l gi tr phn loi. Ni cch khc Hi quy tuyn tnh l mt phng php d on bin ph thuc (Y) da trn gi tr ca bin c lp (X). C th c s dng cho cc trng hp chng ta mun d on mt s lng lin tc.
    • tng thut ton:
      • Tm kim h s gc tha mn tt c cc input m cho ra c output theo tp d liu mu.Ti u m hnh theo OLS.
    • Cc bc thc hin:
      • B1: Chia tp d liu thnh 2 phn,Tp train hun luyn m hnh, tp train dng d on kt qu,thc hin nh gi m hnh tuyn tnh
      • B2: Thc hin kim tra,lc v xa ht cc outlier trnh lm sai m hnh.
      • B3: Thc hin train m hnh l th nht
      • B4: Chn li cc bin c nh hng ln n kt qu m hnh sau khi hun luyn ln 1.
      • B5: S dng cc bin va lc hun luyn ln 2 c kt qu tt hn.
      • B6: Thc hin d on, nh gi m hnh trn tp test_data.
  • 5.2 Logistic regression:
    • Hi quy logistic l mt loi phn tch thng k c s dng d on kt qu ca mt bin ph thuc l bin phn loi (chp nhn, khng chp nhn) v bin ph thuc
    • Mc tiu hi quy logistic tm ra mi lin quan gia bin kt qu v bin ph thuc (c nh hng hay khng) v nh gi m hnh
    • tng thut ton
      • B1: Chia tp d liu thnh 2 phn, tp train hun luyn m hnh, thc hin nh gi m hnh logistic.
      • B2: Thc hin kim tra,lc v xa ht cc outlier trnh lm sai m hnh.
      • B3: Xy dng m hnh logistic v train m hnh.
      • B4: a ra d on vi Response l xc sut kim tra kt qu .
      • B5: xy dng ma trn nhm ln v ng ROC nh gi m hnh.

6. Thc nghim, kt qu, v tho lun (experiments, results, and discussions)

  • 6.1 Linear regression:

  • S dng nguyn l out-of-sample validation nh gi m hnh:

  • R-squared mnh ca m hnh vi s dao ng t 0 n 1.Thng ta s hi vng m hnh ca mnh trn mc ngha 0.5.Ngha l khong 50% ca phng sai bin ph thuc Y d on c t bin c lp X l tt,cn li l sai s m Y khng th d on c t X.Hay l cc bin c lp gii thch c bao nhiu phn trm s thay i hay bin thin trong bin ph thuc. R^2=(TSS-RSS)/TSS

  • Li d on RMSE (Li bnh phng trung bnh gc), biu th chnh lch trung bnh gia cc gi tr kt qu bit c quan st trong d liu th nghim v cc gi tr kt qu d on ca m hnh. RMSE cng thp, m hnh cng tt.

  • Ta thng dng root-mean-square error, = , v n c cng n v vi yi(thc t)

  • RMSE,R-square trn tp train l :155,0.8432.

  • RMSE,R-square trn test: 158,0.89.

    • R-square trn m hnh tp test dng nh gi m hnh cho kt qu cao hn tp train.Cho thy mc gii thch c kt qu theo cc bin tt hn.V c 2 m hnh u cho kt qu trn 0.8 > 0.5,c cho l tt .
    • Ch s RMSE trn tp test cho ra kt qu ln hn trn tp test nhng khng qu ln,sau khi dng cng thc chun ha RMSE bng cch chia cho khong gi tr ca bin d on trn tp test RMSE/(max-min)*100
    • Ta c 0.1 (10%) l kt qu thp,sai s ny c th chp nhn c (RMSE chp nhn c di mc 25%)

  • Cho thy m hnh hi quy tuyn tnh ny l mt m hnh d on tt trn tp test.

    • nh di th hin kt qu trn tp train v test khp nhau khon 90%.

  • m hnh ny,chng em c gng loi b tt c outlier cc bin s nhm xy dng m hnh c kt qu tt nht.Bi v :

    • Cc phn t bt thng (Outliers) c th l nguyn nhn gy ra s vi phm cc gi thit ca m hnh hi quy tuyn tnh v lm mo m kt qu d bo ca m hnh.
    • outliers c nh hng rt mnh n kt quca OLS
    • Loi b outliers theo tiu chun nm ngoi 2 ln lch chun so vi mean phn d

  • 6.2 Logistic regression:

.

  • Theo quan st m hnh, cc bin nh hng n chin dch l: NumWebVisitsMonth NumStorePurchases,MntMeatProducts, MntGoldProds, MntWines,Recency
  • Gii thch m hnh
    • formula = Response l bin phn loi(c hoc khng ) m hnh mi c ngha
    • Trong glm c nhiu lut phn phi, m trong phn phi nh phn (binomial) l mt lut phn phi chun cho hi qui logistic. Do ,family=binomial
    • Deviance Residuals: gii thch phn nh khc bit gia m hnh v d liu
    • Null deviance: m hnh khng c bin phn loi (c hoc khng )
    • Residual deviance: m hnh vi bin phn loi(c hoc khng )
    • Ch bo ng cong AUC th hin kh nng d on ca m hnh vi t l thnh cng l 84%, cho thy m hnh d on kh tt c v m tnh thc v dng tnh thc.
